f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>正常男人望下面就望到自己賓周，但你睇下自己幾撚大個肚腩，本癲狗好心，建議下你照鏡等自己睇到粒賓周仔，點知原來你條傻鳩唔識中文衝出黎柒:</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/324dmgopy7/Screenshot_2017-10-14-10-31-46.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F324dmgopy7%2FScreenshot_2017-10-14-10-31-46.png&h=a28273a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em>肥鳩大隻連解讀中文&ldquo;你照鏡咪知囉懵撚&rdquo;哩句句子都有困難，自己柒左仲要周圍話俾人知，不如學好d中文先出黎教人啦懵撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </em></span></span>"},{"pid":"c7dcdb2cabdbdbf209f6484381ddead831c26c06","tid":509200,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T13:58:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地兩個做咩騎劫人哋個post？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為佢地係食屎狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf20e8b3641ae590414d0e666cd811997e67e974","tid":509200,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T13:59:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">當肥鳩大隻被拆穿其柒點時，就會以話自己&ldquo;假膠&rdquo;同話對方&ldquo;真心膠&rdquo;來為自己辯護，如下圖:</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/huoj9jqeh/Screenshot_2017-09-29-14-11-56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fhuoj9jqeh%2FScreenshot_2017-09-29-14-11-56.png&h=0f10322e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜條傻鳩唔明白一個道理，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係明眼人一睇就知，肥鳩其實就係故事主角既投射</span></span></strong>，例如牠本身又肥又矮，就會引用d主角又肥又矮既故事。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>所以各位都爭相留下正皮，表示對其恥笑及支持本癲狗的撚狗行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"}]}